## Register new User with all the Fields

### Request body fields

*   Name
    *   {type: String, minLength: 3}
*   Bio
    *   {type: String, maxLength: 50 }
*   dob
    *   {type: Date, default: Present Date }
*   Email
    *   {type: String, Unique: True }
*   ProfilePic
    *   {type: String} -- Image in base64 fromat
*   Username
    *   {type: String, Unique: true }
*   Password
    *   {type: String, minLength: 8}

